RECONSIDERATION OF PRIOR DECISIONS

2004-0001. Academy of Medicine of Cincinnati v. Aetna Health, Inc.

Hamilton App. Nos. C-030109, C-030110 and C-030111, 155 Ohio App.3d 310, 2003-Ohio-6194. Reported at 108 Ohio St.3d 185, 2006-Ohio-657, 842 N.E.2d 488. On motion for reconsideration of United Healthcare of Ohio, Inc. Motion denied.
